<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>🗑️ スレッド削除完了</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #f2f2f2;
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
    }
    .card h1 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: #2e7d32;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .card p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      word-break: break-word;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #125ea6;
    }
    .icon {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #2e7d32;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .card h1 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }
      .card p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      .btn {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">✅</div>
    <h1>スレッドを削除しました</h1>
    <p><%= message %></p>
    <a href="/clubs/<%= clubId %>" class="btn">スレッド一覧へ戻る</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
